It may also belong to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as it proposes a distributed algorithm. Additionally, it may belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as it deals with optimization algorithms. It may also belong to cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) as it deals with convergence analysis of optimization algorithms. Finally, it may belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it deals with control and optimization problems.
